    XT60R["XT60-R (6S B)"]
  end

  Aplus --> XT90p --> LOAD --> XT90m --> Bminus
  Aminus -- "K1 (Series Link)" --- Bplus

  Aplus --> XT60L
  Aminus --> XT60L
  Bplus --> XT60R
  Bminus --> XT60R
